快就会在此仪表板上看到 VR 作为一种新的设备类型，以及桌面、移动设备、平板电脑和控制台。</p><p> Meta 最近将操作 Quest 耳机的最低年龄从 13 岁降低到 10 岁，但这一变化不会影响<em>Roblox</em> 。您必须年满 13 岁才能在 VR 中使用该应用程序。考虑到该游戏的成瘾性以及<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-didnt-want-roblox-on-playstation-due-to-child-safety-concerns-200631635.html"><ins>相关的儿童安全问题，这可能是最好的选择。</ins></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/roblox-is-coming-to-meta-quest-vr-headsets-181633766.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/roblox-is-coming-to-meta-quest-vr-headsets-181633766.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4edfbea8-7251-40f6-a34a-691d4d530b76</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 18:16:33 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689185794</ingested><modified> 2023-07-12T18:16:38+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="773" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/8f8e2180-20da-11ee-bbef-49703c97dbed" width="1375"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="773" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/8f8e2180-20da-11ee-bbef-49703c97dbed" width="1375"><media:media_html><